{
  "texts": [
    "For example, possible items (but not items actually on the test) would include, \" [2, 5, 11, None, 35, 71] (answer: 23),\" \" [3, 4, 8, 10, 13, None ]\" (answer: 16), and \" [2, 12, 17, 68, 71, None ]\" (answer: 142).",
    "In high-stakes settings, the test's time limit is 17 minutes.",
    "The test manual reports the test's internal consistency α =.70 and test-retest reliability =.62.",
    "The test converged r =.58 and r =.62 with other commercial numerical reasoning tests.",
    "Additionally, the test converged r =.61 with a number-letter series test and r =.60 with a 3D rotation test from the International Cognitive Ability Resource (ICAR, 2014)."
  ]
}